## Create a new page
POST http://localhost:3000/api/pages HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "title": "test page published",
    "author": "user",
    "publicationDate": "2023-04-04"
}
###

## Get all pages
GET http://localhost:3000/api/pages HTTP/1.1
###

## Get all published pages
GET http://localhost:3000/api/pages/published HTTP/1.1
###

## Get all pages by the user logged in
GET http://localhost:3000/api/author/user/pages HTTP/1.1
###

## Get a specific page
GET http://localhost:3000/api/pages/2 HTTP/1.1
###

## Get a specific page (expect 404)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/pages/0 HTTP/1.1
###

## Get a published page
GET http://localhost:3000/api/pages/published/3 HTTP/1.1
###

## Get a published page (expect error)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/pages/published/1 HTTP/1.1
###

## Create a new block
POST http://localhost:3000/api/pages/4/blocks HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "type": "header",
    "content": "this is the header",
    "position": 1
}
###